{"tid":1851403,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解呢間bnm.com.hk愛心寶寶黑店仲未收皮","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T03:03:22.000Z","uid":226014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"261e9bdd693756a3c8ead57b1978854edbbf0416","tid":1851403,"uid":226014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"啲貨幾個月都未收到 無晒貨仲要唔退錢 迫人換佢間鋪啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到咁多人同佢買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知幾時先拎到貨<br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n九龍灣啓興道2號太平洋貿易中心<br />\n16樓14-15室<br />\n<br />\n旺角豉油街15號萬利商業大廈<br />\n5樓全層<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGS4pAk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGS4pAk.png&h=b70df1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPV5TtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPV5TtH.png&h=df94d3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCMMCVo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCMMCVo.png&h=f7a8fb42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ys76OL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ys76OL.png&h=a4f5e5d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOaQ4C6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOaQ4C6.png&h=8d003753&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43c2fd7de6ae0c79b81986bec12a89f95d53f9af","tid":1851403,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"ff7d1c86720b5a8b42a08d6576255bf9c0bbdde9","tid":1851403,"uid":226014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{